trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"></xref> objects in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje kolekcję <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"> </xref> obiekty w <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: The DataGridItemCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> objects, which in turn represent the data items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control.
trans-unit.target: Klasa DataGridItemCollection reprezentuje kolekcję <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>obiektów, które z kolei zawierają elementy danych w <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontroli.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically retrieve <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> objects from a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control, use one of following methods: - Use the indexer to get a single <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> object from the collection, using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Programowo pobrać <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>obiektów z <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontrolować, użyj jednej z następujących metod:-Użyj indeksatora, aby pobrać pojedynczy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>obiekt z kolekcji przy użyciu tablicy notacji.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the collection to a <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Użyj <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>metody, aby skopiować zawartość kolekcji do <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, które mogą następnie służyć do uzyskania elementu z kolekcji.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> interface, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Użyj <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>metodę w celu utworzenia <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>interfejsu, którego można użyć do uzyskania elementu z kolekcji.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.Count%2A> property specifies the total number of items in the collection and is commonly used to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.Count%2A>Właściwość określa całkowitą liczbę elementów w kolekcji i jest najczęściej używany do określenia górna granica kolekcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Ten konstruktor umożliwia tworzenie i inicjuje nowe wystąpienie <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>klasy.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"></xref> that contains the items with which to initialize the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"> </xref> zawiera elementy, z którą ma zostać zainicjowania dla kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: Copies all the items from this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"></xref> collection to the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, starting at the specified index in the <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Kopiuje wszystkie elementy z tej <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"> </xref> kolekcji do określonego <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, rozpoczynając od określonego indeksu w <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to copy the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> collection into the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, starting at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Ta metoda umożliwia skopiowanie zawartości <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>kolekcji w określonym <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>, rozpoczynając od określonego indeksu.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `array` parameter must be a zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > `array` Parametr musi być liczony od zera <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> that receives the copied items from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Liczony od zera <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> odbierająca skopiowane elementy z <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first position in the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> to receive the copied contents.
trans-unit.target: Pierwszą pozycję w określonym <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> do odbierania skopiowane dane.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera liczbę <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"> </xref> obiektów w kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: Use the Count property to determine the number of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Umożliwia określenie liczby właściwości <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>obiekty w <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>kolekcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>

trans-unit.source: The Count property is commonly used when iterating through the collection to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość Count jest najczęściej używany do określenia górna granica kolekcji podczas iteracji w kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: The number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Liczba <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"> </xref> obiektów w kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object that contains all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Zwraca <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-zaimplementowany obiekt, który zawiera wszystkie <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"> </xref> obiekty w <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"> </xref> kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object that can be iterated through to get each item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Ta metoda służy do tworzenia <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-zaimplementowany obiekt, który należy powtórzyć za pomocą można pobrać każdego elementu w <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection>kolekcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to get the item currently pointed to in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Użyj <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>właściwości do pobrania elementu obecnie wskazywana w kolekcji.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Użyj <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metody, aby przejść do następnego elementu w kolekcji.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to its initial position.
trans-unit.target: Użyj <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metodę, aby przenieść modułu wyliczającego do pozycji początkowej.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > After you create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object or use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to the first item in the collection, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Po utworzeniu <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-zaimplementowany obiekt lub użyj <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metodę, aby przenieść modułu wyliczającego do pierwszego elementu w kolekcji, należy wywołać <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metody.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the item represented by the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: W przeciwnym razie element reprezentowany przez <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>właściwość jest niezdefiniowana.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object that contains all <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-zaimplementowany obiekt, który zawiera wszystkie <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem"> </xref> obiekty w <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItemCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property is derived from the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> interface and is overridden to always return `false`.
